HEADWORD: Blindness
<hw>Blind"ness</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>State or
condition of being blind, literally or figuratively.</def>
<rj><au>Darwin.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Color blindness</b></col>, <cd>inability to distinguish
certain color. See <er>Daltonism</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blind reader</ent>⟦br⟧
